{"tid":177473,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英格蘭成功幫冰島提升出生率！！！！","createTime":"2017-03-29T01:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T12:39:11.000Z","uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4281620d4e06367cf2f6ba24ca1c7a8c4bca17f","tid":177473,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=46991403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】去年歐洲國家盃，小國冰島爆出冷門，殺退英格蘭晉級8強，創造歷史，想不到9個月後餘波未了，嬰兒潮正在全國爆發。<br />\n<br />\n冰島雜誌《Visir》披露，人口33萬的冰島，目前正被大規模的嬰兒潮困擾，出生人數屢創新高，醫院應接不暇。<br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問，冰島人為了慶祝國家隊殺入8強，情侶和夫妻在比賽之後加緊「操練」，腎上腺素飆升，連場「激戰」，導致9個月後的初生嬰兒急增。<br />\n<br />\n一位麻醉科醫生彼德透過社交網表示：「本周末接受無痛分娩的孕婦打破全國紀錄，一切發生在冰島2:1擊敗英格蘭之役的9個月後。」"},{"pid":"dacd8cf1e7bbf8b378939cf780ae9f2f5097e973","tid":177473,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分秒秒內射"},{"pid":"0b1ae5c5acd2c42cfbbcf209349dca75198b67de","tid":177473,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14bd670413624d8a50c3b8e129352f5fa6d3fe9","tid":177473,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"兩夫妻一齊唱跳維京人舞<br />\n之後激戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aba925c5cf188b1e1c9b9e6dc862d61d655e04","tid":177473,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:38:03.000Z","msg":"香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94374e355263e852895547a68b6c05c4c193f4b0","tid":177473,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017